"1 1/2 cups chicken broth","1 cup dried morel mushrooms (or other dried mushrooms)","8  skinless chicken thighs (or a combination of legs and thighs)","3/4 teaspoon salt, divided","2  slices smoked bacon, diced","1/2 cup white wine","1 1/2 cups whipping cream","2 tablespoons Dijon mustard","4  shallots, chopped","3  baby leeks or green onions","1 pound fingerling or new potatoes, peeled and cut into 1/2-inch slices","4  garlic cloves","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground pepper","1 tablespoon chopped fresh tarragon","1 tablespoon chopped fresh chives","1 tablespoon chopped fresh parsley"